msItem.title: Three treatises on astronomy and arithmetic

respStmt.persName: ʻAbd al-Ghanī ibn ʻAbd al-Qādir Qāyinī, active 1619
عبد الغني بن عبد القادر قايني،
Muḥammad Riḍā ibn ʻAbd Allāh, active 1782

msItem.title: Īn risālah ast dar ʻilm-i ḥisāb

supportDesc.extent: ii, 125, iii leaves : 220 x 122 (142 x 60) mm, bound to 220 x 124 mm

layoutDesc.layout: 12 long lines; catchwords every verso, lower left; border-ruled.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in clear nastaʻliq in black ink; pointed.

decoDesc.decoNote: Numerous diagrams in red and black; textblock border-ruled in blue and gold; rubrications in red; some pages gold sprinkled over textblock.

binding.p: Brown leather (Type III) with gilt-stamped central mandorla with two pendants on the vertical axis; gold-tooled frame; bright red doublure.

origin.p: Copy completed in Shaʻbān of the year 1028 AH (1619 CE) by ʻAbd al-Ghanī ibn ʻAbd al-Qādir Qāyinī (f. 68r, 69r, 125r).

history.provenance: Formerly owner by Muḥammad Riḍā ibn ʻAbd Allāh in 1196? AH (1782 CE) (stamps f. 68r, 69r, 125v).
